{"tid":1105171,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《復仇者聯盟4》片場寡姐美隊聯機玩GameBoy","createTime":"2019-04-13T16:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T16:31:00.000Z","uid":173952,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5b8d730096ab2dc357c9c66ff46e3eb9fc54bb4f","tid":1105171,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHMKOgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjHMKOgH.jpg&h=1ab4e201&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c1e62701ed87126b29244b3aba78596784355b4","tid":1105171,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:41:47.000Z","msg":"眼看著《復仇者聯盟4》即將上映，不知道各位有沒有搶到首映的票呢？最近在電影中扮演Hulk的馬克在推特上放出了一張幕後照：黑寡婦斯嘉麗和美隊克里斯在一起用任天堂GameBoy聯機打遊戲。有玩家從背面的卡帶認出了兩人玩的正是經典的《俄羅斯方塊》，有粉絲調侃道，對於設定上誕生於1920年的美隊來說，1989年發售的GB可是個新鮮玩意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  GameBoy手提遊戲機對於很多歐美玩家可以說是不折不扣的童年，這款由橫井軍平設計的手提遊戲機兼顧了便捷性和趣味性，兼之出色的續航能力，一經推出就征服了全世界的玩家。黑寡婦和美隊兩位一起聯機對戰的場景也觸動了《God of War》總監Cory Barlog的心弦，他轉發了這條推特，並表示自己也想把GameBoy找出來玩玩了。"},{"pid":"7fbc0dde98da1ecd1d9e0d1187077cb6d182259f","tid":1105171,"uid":125380,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KMEbWVSmIiemObS5BUKMbQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjU1O2g9NDU4/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/heawork.tumblr.com/065bb0b5aae104cc8aee2216a5af9177\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FKMEbWVSmIiemObS5BUKMbQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjU1O2g9NDU4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fheawork.tumblr.com%2F065bb0b5aae104cc8aee2216a5af9177&h=391913c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"453225f822a858ca1304e59ef0e59df877342e5b","tid":1105171,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:43:46.000Z","msg":"仲開到機？我果部入帶冇反應了"},{"pid":"75c6ecad6f0019c65a57d23a5fd05d311bbb8fc1","